{"tid":1547764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出返嚟先知網上話佢死咗，嗰晚有同佢傾過幾句","createTime":"2019-09-06T18:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:06:16.000Z","uid":291405,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"126f0aeec115470e655d932d9d05ebdf323fe556","tid":1547764,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"8.31太子傳死訊 戰友報平安<br />\n<br />\n(沒有事? 我懷疑受訪者認錯人﹐當了另一人是在地上沒有知覺那位)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網上盛傳8.31於太子站月台被速龍警員按倒地上施襲、懷疑失去知覺的男子已經死亡，但同在當晚被捕的阿俊（化名）向《蘋果》表示，在扣查時曾與該男子傾談，有講有笑，無見到他有明顯傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n當中就有《蘋果》當日直播影片中被兩名速龍警員按倒在地上、再用警棍攻擊的男子，「出返嚟先知網上話佢死咗，嗰晚有同佢傾過幾句，平安嘅，行得走得，唔覺有咩明顯傷，仲有講有笑」。但他未有留意該男子幾時離開警署，「係保釋定送去第二度真係唔知」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190905/20762561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762561&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2rXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=9a4a277c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762561&h=ec43f756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190905/20762561</a><br />\n~~~"},{"pid":"67bef6c84d189e28ce7cf50b3e719562377d6487","tid":1547764,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a01e7c0015fe34ae2427669367c78d5abe3e39ff","tid":1547764,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:57:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"be1a08b3946f56124e42e092446a32fb70075fcf","tid":1547764,"uid":31545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:32:05.000Z","msg":"咁樣無錢"},{"pid":"6934e0d635fc89b9d